download '.iso' and use rufus to move it into a USB
back up the files in /C:/user/yanyi...
restart the PC with constantly pressing F12 and enter BIOS setup
click SATA Operator and switch RAID ON to AHCI
click secure boot to make sure the secure boot enable is not checked
again use F12 but choose the UEFI BOOT option which is the USB
enter the setup of linux
